{"tid":2288800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武警女兵全身放滿蚯蚓練「人槍合一」　網民嘆：值得我託付終身","createTime":"2020-11-16T18:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T04:24:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"541e14eb64dff71ba26191853b050805240f96f6","tid":2288800,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"央視近日發布武警的訓練影片，顯示兩名武警特戰女兵為了進行抗干擾訓練，全身放滿了蚯蚓。影片播出後，在網上引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n央視欄目《軍事紀實》12日發布的影片顯示，兩名特戰女兵進行抗干擾訓練，其中一名女兵跪在地上當做狙擊槍基底，另一名女兵則進行瞄準射擊，兩人都必須保持定力，讓姿勢不變。引人注目的是，訓練時兩人手上、耳朵上、狙擊槍上爬滿了蚯蚓。<br />\n<br />\n長官更在槍上疊放了多個空彈殼，只要子彈掉下一個，訓練就要延長1分鐘時間。兩名女兵原本10分鐘的訓練，經過調整狀態，最後經過18分鐘，才達成「人槍合一」。節目聲稱，狙擊手身為戰場幽靈，「不僅要有隱蔽殺敵的本領，還要具備在惡劣戰場環境中悄然潛伏的能力」。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名女兵坦言，訓練當下已經感受不到腳的存在了，撐住身體的手肘，一開始是痛，後來沒有感覺了。<br />\n<br />\n這段「蟲蟲訓練法」引發外界討論，不少網民稱讚女兵英勇；但也有人看後稱「各種作秀」、「這種訓練真的有用嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n「真的是霸氣，我一男孩子都受不了。而且我對這樣的女生很動心，甚至都想軍婚了。她們那樣霸氣，值得我託付終身，一定會保護好我。」<br />\n「我的天哪！我的雞皮疙瘩！女兵真牛！」<br />\n「蟲蟲爬到耳朵，鼻子裡沒事嗎？」<br />\n「厲害，我想想就覺得害怕。」<br />\n「是我的話，估計當場去世，最怕軟體動物了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405041999859683328708139.jpeg/sU1I2GTVeCGGVxczVSZf3hhU4w3bxe7U2ZPaH9mT2h8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405041999859683328708139.jpeg%2FsU1I2GTVeCGGVxczVSZf3hhU4w3bxe7U2ZPaH9mT2h8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f277da5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405042018672185344410392.jpeg/gadXD3_mGFQfamyiM_A2koqpRd-ARidRLOQ_BizkPwY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405042018672185344410392.jpeg%2FgadXD3_mGFQfamyiM_A2koqpRd-ARidRLOQ_BizkPwY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fca4b7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405042002070212608608529.jpeg/jxY6PSql2R5fm-1ZaDBnVvmjLus2EBdrdRnPh3UZz4c?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405042002070212608608529.jpeg%2FjxY6PSql2R5fm-1ZaDBnVvmjLus2EBdrdRnPh3UZz4c%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ce864712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405042020517810176193472.jpeg/vUoueRVvNIQwHlF6dqE5MU0oKV5-N07sa967eGveu3g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405042020517810176193472.jpeg%2FvUoueRVvNIQwHlF6dqE5MU0oKV5-N07sa967eGveu3g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=67485cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405042014532145152809312.jpeg/BILI90vq03XkhOj2-CUKLSwBjsgcvKdN6RqzHukasx4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405042014532145152809312.jpeg%2FBILI90vq03XkhOj2-CUKLSwBjsgcvKdN6RqzHukasx4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ce107eb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a865fadd2d19917e9cee959fc27875c58db578a8","tid":2288800,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"有自殘傾向嗎"},{"pid":"253e420bbf25bebaf2adc064e0fd40bce3d8292a","tid":2288800,"uid":85586,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"訓練用嚟射返自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312423d87721e66f6605005ae8ec57fe920d7dc1","tid":2288800,"uid":276839,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"明明男人黎"},{"pid":"373002f6a4e147a380ea5e19420f440459c591a7","tid":2288800,"uid":43173,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gnrre9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnrre9w.jpg&h=f829ea6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e18d1ab998e6e8f340feb11606d4489f7caf9d6d","tid":2288800,"uid":361975,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11